rk_run_metrics/\\n```\\n\\n### `script_run_metrics/`\\n\\nStores metrics from regular script runs in `metadata-forge`.\\n\\n- Each AI script has a `JSON` file named after the script.\\n- Each object in the `JSON` will represent metrics of one run for a single library version.\\n- Example:\\n  - `script_run_metrics/new_library_support.json` – metrics for a script that manages or tests adding new library support.\\n\\n### `benchmark_run_metrics/`\\n\\nStores metrics from predefined benchmark configurations.\\n\\n- Each benchmark has a JSON file named after it.\\n- Example:\\n  - `benchmark_run_metrics/metadata_entries_hunter.json` – metrics for a benchmark suite that tracks performance or behavior when adding new library support, using a strategy that favors generating tests which tend to cover as many metadata entries as possible.\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_26\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,240p' /home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2098-57b08261/script_run_metrics/fix_javac_fail.json\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_26\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,240p' /home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2098-57b08261/script_run_metrics/fix_javac_fail.json\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"[\\n  {\\n    \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"2026-03-13T16:20:26Z\\\",\\n    \\\"library\\\": \\\"io.grpc:grpc-netty:1.77.1\\\",\\n    \\\"strategy_name\\\": \\\"javac_iterative\\\",\\n    \\\"status\\\": \\\"failure\\\",\\n    \\\"metrics\\\": {\\n      \\\"input_tokens_used\\\": 2129,\\n      \\\"output_tokens_used\\\": 91,\\n      \\\"iterations\\\": 1,\\n      \\\"cost_usd\\\": 0.0,\\n      \\\"generated_loc\\\": 0,\\n      \\\"tested_library_loc\\\": 0,\\n  